postBodyContent: Hmmm, yes, I’ve just decided that Buffy Summers is dyslexic and was never properly diagnosed. Buffy Summers switched schools in the middle of the year, had to play catch up on a semester’s worth of material, saved the world on a daily basis, kicked ass on the SATs, and was accepted into a tier 1 university (talking about Northwestern, not UC Sunnydale), all while struggling with an undiagnosed learning disability. Literally when will any of your faves.
May the Force of others be with you.
